# âœ… Angular To-Do App Assignment

A simple and modular Angular application with **Login**, **Signup**, and a **To-Do List**. Built using Angular, this app implements user authentication, reactive form validations, task filtering, searching, and local storage persistence.

---

## ğŸ“¦ Features

### ğŸ‘¤ Signup Page
- Full Name, Email, Password, Confirm Password
- Validations:
  - All fields are required
  - Email must be valid
  - Password must be at least 6 characters
  - Confirm Password must match
- On success: Save user to localStorage and redirect to login

### ğŸ” Login Page
- Fields: Email, Password
- Validations:
  - Required fields
  - Valid email format
- Authenticate using stored credentials
- On success: Redirect to To-Do page
- On failure: Show error message

### âœ… To-Do List Page
- Add Task (Title required, Description & Due Date optional)
- List separates:
  - Pending Tasks
  - Completed Tasks
- Toggle complete/incomplete
- Delete tasks
- Persist tasks in localStorage

### ğŸ” Bonus (Optional)
- Search tasks by title
- Filter: All / Completed / Pending
- Sort tasks by due date

---

## âš™ï¸ Technologies Used
- Angular (v17+)
- TypeScript
- Reactive Forms
- HTML5 + CSS3
- Local Storage for persistence

